        <section class="docs-section animate-on-scroll">
            <h2 class="section-title">Getting Access to our Projects</h2>
            <div class="section-content">
                <h3>Linking your Roblox account with AGS</h3>
                <p>Submit your Roblox username:</p>
                <ul class="steps-list">
                    <li>Go to the Discord and do /linkroblox-staff</li>
                    <li>Enter your Roblox username in the pop-up</li>
                    <li>Wait for a Development Manager to link your account</li>
                    <li>You will recieve a DM with the status of your access request</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Opening the Project</h3>
                <p>To open up one of our Roblox Studio Projects:</p>
                <ul class="steps-list">
                    <li>Open up Roblox Studio</li>
                    <li>Click on the project you have been tasked with working on</li>
                    <li>The project should open up, and you are ready to work!</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

